---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="保护团队AI数据安全">

  <style>
    /* ── Hero ── */
    .hero {
      padding: 140px 40px 100px; max-width: var(--max-width); margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; align-items: center;
      position: relative;
    }
    .hero-text {
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
    }
    .hero-text .eyebrow {
      font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: var(--green-muted); margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .hero-text h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5vw, 3.8rem); font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.06; letter-spacing: -0.04em; margin-bottom: 28px;
      color: #f0f0f5;
    }
    .hero-text h1 em {
      font-style: normal; color: var(--green);
    }
    .hero-text .lead {
      font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 40px; max-width: 440px;
    }
    .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 56px; }
    .hero-stat {
      display: flex; gap: 48px;
    }
    .hero-stat div {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    }
    .hero-stat b { font-size: 1.6rem; color: #f0f0f5; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    .hero-stat span { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-quiet); margin-top: 2px; }

    .hero-visual { position: relative; }
    .hero-glow {
      position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
      width: 480px; height: 480px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(163,230,53,0.04) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero-code {
      background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden;
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
    }
    .hero-code .bar {
      display: flex; gap: 6px; padding: 14px 18px;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .hero-code .bar span { width: 9px; height: 9px; border-radius: 9px; }
    .hero-code .bar span:nth-child(1) { background: #ef4444; }
    .hero-code .bar span:nth-child(2) { background: #f59e0b; }
    .hero-code .bar span:nth-child(3) { background: #22c55e; }
    .hero-code pre {
      background: transparent; border: none; padding: 22px 24px;
      font-size: 0.82rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--text-dim);
      overflow-x: auto; font-family: 'Fira Code', 'Cascadia Code', 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    }
    .hero-code pre .c1 { color: var(--green); }
    .hero-code pre .c2 { color: var(--text-quiet); }
    .hero-code pre .c3 { color: var(--amber); }

    /* ── Problem — clean 3-col ── */
    .section-problem { background: var(--paper); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .problem-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 56px;
      max-width: var(--max-width); margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .problem-item .num {
      font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-quiet);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .problem-item h3 { font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: #f0f0f5; }
    .problem-item p { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.65; }

    /* ── Features — refined bento ── */
    .bento {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1px;
      max-width: var(--max-width); margin: 0 auto;
      background: var(--border);
    }
    .bento-item {
      background: var(--paper); padding: 48px 40px;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    }
    .bento-item.main { grid-column: span 2; grid-row: span 2; }
    .bento-item .icon {
      width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: var(--radius);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 22px; font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .bento-item .icon.green { background: var(--green-bg); color: var(--green-muted); }
    .bento-item .icon.purple { background: var(--purple-bg); color: var(--purple); }
    .bento-item .icon.amber { background: var(--amber-bg); color: var(--amber); }
    .bento-item h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: #f0f0f5; }
    .bento-item p { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6; }

    /* ── How it works ── */
    .steps {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 64px;
      max-width: var(--max-width); margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .step {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    }
    .step .step-icon {
      width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: var(--radius);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 24px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .step:nth-child(1) .step-icon { background: var(--green-bg); border-color: rgba(163,230,53,0.15); color: var(--green); }
    .step:nth-child(2) .step-icon { background: var(--purple-bg); border-color: rgba(167,139,250,0.15); color: var(--purple); }
    .step:nth-child(3) .step-icon { background: var(--amber-bg); border-color: rgba(245,158,11,0.15); color: var(--amber); }
    .step h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: #f0f0f5; }
    .step p { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.65; }

    /* ── Pricing ── */
    .pricing-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px;
      max-width: 880px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .pricing-card {
      background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 40px 36px;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .pricing-card:hover { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); }
    .pricing-card.featured {
      border-color: rgba(163,230,53,0.2);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(163,230,53,0.03), transparent);
    }
    .pricing-card .plan-name {
      font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      color: var(--text-quiet); margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .pricing-card .price {
      font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      margin-bottom: 28px; color: #f0f0f5;
    }
    .pricing-card .price span { font-size: 0.3em; font-weight: 400; color: var(--text-dim); margin-left: 2px; }
    .pricing-card ul { list-style: none; margin-bottom: 32px; flex: 1; }
    .pricing-card li {
      padding: 7px 0; color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 0.9rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
    }
    .pricing-card li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .pricing-card li.yes::before { content: ""; display: none; }
    .pricing-card li.no { color: var(--text-quiet); }
    .pricing-card .btn { width: 100%; }
    .badge-featured {
      position: absolute; top: -11px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
      background: var(--green-muted); color: #0a0a0a; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600;
      padding: 4px 16px; border-radius: 100px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }

    /* ── FAQ ── */
    .faq-list { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .faq-item { padding: 26px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft); }
    .faq-item:first-child { border-top: 1px solid var(--border-soft); }
    .faq-item h4 { font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; font-size: 1.02rem; }
    .faq-item p { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.65; }

    /* ── CTA ── */
    .section-cta { background: var(--paper); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .cta-content { text-align: center; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .cta-content h2 { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .cta-content p { color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 36px; font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .cta-content .actions { display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; padding: 80px 24px 60px; }
      .hero-stat { gap: 32px; }
      .problem-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
      .bento { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .bento-item.main { grid-column: span 1; grid-row: span 1; }
      .steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
      .pricing-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>

  <!-- ── Hero ── -->
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <div class="eyebrow">AI DATA PRIVACY INFRASTRUCTURE</div>
      <h1>团队的 AI 数据保护，<em>一行代码不改</em></h1>
      <p class="lead">本地反向代理自动脱敏手机号、身份证、邮箱、银行卡，再发送给 ChatGPT / DeepSeek / Claude。30 秒部署，数据不出网。</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/download" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">免费下载</a>
        <a href="/docs/quickstart" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">查看文档</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <div><b>&lt; 50ms</b> <span>请求延迟</span></div>
        <div><b>本地部署</b> <span>数据不出网</span></div>
        <div><b>开源</b> <span>代码可审计</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-visual">
      <div class="hero-glow"></div>
      <div class="hero-code">
        <div class="bar"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
        <pre><span class="c2"># 一行 Docker，启动本地防火墙</span>
<span class="c1">$</span> docker run -d -p 9999:9999 \
  ghcr.io/gunxueqiu6/ai-privacy-gateway:lite

<span class="c2"># 发送请求 — 敏感信息自动脱敏</span>
<span class="c1">$</span> curl http://localhost:9999/v1/chat \
  -d <span class="c3">'{'{'}"model":"deepseek-chat"{'}'}'</span>

<span class="c2"># 手机号 → &lt;PHONE_7a3f&gt;
# 身份证 → &lt;ID_9b2e&gt;
# AI 响应时自动还原，用户无感知</span></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── Problem ── -->
  <section class="section-problem">
    <div class="section-head">
      <h2>你的团队每天都在泄露什么</h2>
      <p>99% 的团队在用真实生产数据调试 AI，却不知道这些数据正被发往境外。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="problem-grid">
      <div class="problem-item">
        <div class="num">01</div>
        <h3>IDE 里粘贴真实手机号</h3>
        <p>开发者在 Cursor / Copilot 中用真实数据调试，代码补全将敏感信息发送到境外服务器。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-item">
        <div class="num">02</div>
        <h3>客服机器人泄露客户隐私</h3>
        <p>飞书 / 钉钉机器人通过 AI API 处理工单，客户手机号、邮箱原文传输，无任何脱敏措施。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-item">
        <div class="num">03</div>
        <h3>训练数据被 AI 公司采集</h3>
        <p>发给 ChatGPT / DeepSeek 的业务数据可能用于模型训练，竞品次日就能问出你的商业机密。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Features (bento) ── -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-head">
      <h2>全面防护，零侵入</h2>
      <p>不改代码，不换框架，只改一个 URL 地址。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bento">
      <div class="bento-item main">
        <div class="icon green">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>自动检测 · 手机号 · 身份证 · 邮箱 · 银行卡</h3>
        <p>内置正则引擎 + 自定义敏感词库，自动识别并替换所有敏感字段。支持中文姓名、公司名、项目代号等任意自定义关键词，可配置正则模式。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-item">
        <div class="icon purple">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>SSE 流式透传</h3>
        <p>Streaming 响应实时脱敏还原，零延迟，用户完全无感知。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-item">
        <div class="icon amber">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>本地存储 · 数据不出网</h3>
        <p>映射表仅存本地 SQLite，绝不上传云端。一键销毁：<code>rm -rf vault_data/</code></p>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-item">
        <div class="icon green">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>5 分钟上线</h3>
        <p>API 地址从 api.openai.com 改为 localhost:9999，其他完全不变。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-item">
        <div class="icon purple">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>拦截统计 & 审计</h3>
        <p>实时拦截数、字段分类、会话追溯，满足合规审计要求。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-item">
        <div class="icon amber">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>云端规则更新</h3>
        <p>Pro 版支持敏感词规则库自动更新，新威胁即时响应。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── How it works ── -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-head">
      <h2>工作原理</h2>
      <p>请求到达 → 脱敏 → 转发 → AI 响应 → 还原。全程透明。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-icon">1</div>
        <h3>检测</h3>
        <p>正则引擎 + 关键词匹配自动识别请求中所有敏感字段。支持自定义正则和团队专属词库。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-icon">2</div>
        <h3>脱敏</h3>
        <p>原始数据替换为占位符，映射关系写入本地 SQLite。脱敏后的请求转发至上游 AI API。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-icon">3</div>
        <h3>还原</h3>
        <p>AI 响应返回时，占位符自动还原为原始数据。对用户完全透明，无感知体验。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Pricing ── -->
  <section id="pricing">
    <div class="section-head">
      <h2>版本</h2>
      <p>从个人到企业，选择适合你的防护等级。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pricing-grid" style="position:relative">
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <div class="plan-name">LITE 个人版</div>
        <div class="price">免费</div>
        <ul>
          <li class="yes">正则脱敏（手机/邮箱/身份证/银行卡）</li>
          <li class="yes">流式代理 + SSE 缓冲</li>
          <li class="yes">自定义敏感词</li>
          <li class="yes">基础管理后台</li>
          <li class="no">多人并发</li>
          <li class="no">团队看板</li>
          <li class="no">云端规则更新</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/download" class="btn btn-outline">免费下载</a>
      </div>

      <div class="pricing-card featured" style="position:relative">
        <div class="badge-featured">推荐</div>
        <div class="plan-name">PRO 团队版</div>
        <div class="price">&yen;99<span>/月</span></div>
        <ul>
          <li class="yes">全部 Lite 功能</li>
          <li class="yes">20 人并发 WAL 模式</li>
          <li class="yes">团队看板 + 会话查询</li>
          <li class="yes">云端规则自动更新</li>
          <li class="yes">日/周/月统计报告</li>
          <li class="yes">邮件技术支持</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">即将上线</a>
      </div>

      <div class="pricing-card">
        <div class="plan-name">ENTERPRISE</div>
        <div class="price">定制<span>年费</span></div>
        <ul>
          <li class="yes">全部 Pro 功能</li>
          <li class="yes">100+ 人高并发</li>
          <li class="yes">Redis 集群存储</li>
          <li class="yes">AC 自动机（万级词库）</li>
          <li class="yes">审计日志 + 告警</li>
          <li class="yes">RBAC 权限控制</li>
          <li class="yes">驻场支持 + SLA</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="mailto:sales@aiprivacygateway.com" class="btn btn-outline">联系我们</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── FAQ ── -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-head">
      <h2>常见问题</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>如何接入？</h4>
        <p>只需将 AI 客户端的 API 地址从 https://api.openai.com 改为 http://localhost:9999，其他完全不变。5 分钟搞定。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>数据安全吗？</h4>
        <p>敏感映射表仅存储在你自己的服务器上（本地 SQLite），不上传任何云端。部署在自己内网，物理隔离。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>支持哪些 AI 服务？</h4>
        <p>所有兼容 OpenAI API 格式的服务：ChatGPT、DeepSeek、Claude、Cursor、Copilot、通义千问、飞书 AI 等。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>如何部署？</h4>
        <p>Docker 一行启动：<code>docker run -d -p 9999:9999 ghcr.io/gunxueqiu6/ai-privacy-gateway:lite</code>。也提供 Windows / macOS 单文件版本。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>Pro 版如何激活？</h4>
        <p>购买后收到 License Key，在管理后台填写激活。License 绑定硬件指纹，防止滥用。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── CTA ── -->
  <section class="section-cta">
    <div class="cta-content">
      <h2>给团队 AI 数据装上防火墙</h2>
      <p>免费 Lite 版，永久可用。不需要信用卡。</p>
      <div class="actions">
        <a href="/download" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">免费下载</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/gunxueqiu6/ai-privacy-gateway" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
